<br>
Transons Elemental Infusion and Veil of the Elements can both be had fairly easily by camping the wild underbulks in Fungus Grove. They have no faction and are non aggro, however they are social so you gotta watch out for repop. Bring a chanter/bard/shaman with you for slow. Eventually you'll have a nice stack of level 52 &amp; 54 spells for various classes. NOTE: oddly enough only the underbulk hatchlings and small underbulks drop spells, the underbulks are always empty albeit good xp.<br>
<br>
Transons Elemental Infusion is level 52, Veil of the Elements is level 54. <p>&lt;Crispin' Critters for Mithaniel Marr since 29MY1999&gt;<br>
